CTF_SKYRAIL

A map remake from 007 NightfireTM.

Let me just get this out of the way before I mention anything else: This is NOT the final version of the map, this is only the early beta version, I still need to do a load of work on the displacements, and clear up the odd texture here and there.

SPECIAL THANKS TO THE FOLLOWING:

PowPew – For extensive beta testing :D. -:Steve-o:- - For helping me with a fat ‘ol compile error I had that almost killed of this project and for joining the 2 bases up with displacements (You rock!) Rebell - For creating such an awesome Capture the Flap mod for CS:S :D (http://www.fpsbanana.com/tools/839) THEnub - For the awesome turret prefabs! Everyone who worked on the original Nightfire - If you’re reading this, you did a great job on that game and thanks for all the great times I had playing that game (and for not suing me for copyright xD).

THIS MAP ALSO WORKS REALLY WELL WITH:

Rebell's CS:S ctf mod - http://www.fpsbanana.com/tools/839 Mango's Artic Skin from Nightfire - http://www.fpsbanana.com/skins/11951
